Titolo: Lode Runner's Rescue

Anno: 1985

Descrizione: Lode Runner's Rescue is a 1985 action game developed by Joshua Scholar for the  Commodore 64 and Atari 8-bit family as a follow-up to Doug Smiths's Lode Runner. Lode Runner was published by Broderbund, but the sequel was published under the Synapse Software name, a company acquired by Broderbund in 1984. Lode Runner's Rescue uses isometric projection to give a 3D feel.